{"tid":2278174,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"33歲拿尼無解罰球 ! 一頭紫髮+龜波氣功慶祝 卻遭絕殺","createTime":"2020-11-09T03:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T05:28:01.000Z","uid":53121,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c455791dd9e065b572cb7ff757fe63ae6e83870c","tid":2278174,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"在今天早上結束的一場美職聯常規賽中，奧蘭多城主場2-3不敵納什維爾。即將34歲的拿尼為主隊射進一個罰球，他在進球後用&ldquo;龜波氣功&rdquo;來進行慶祝。但終場前的兩個丟球，卻使得奧蘭多城最終2-3遭遇逆轉絕殺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFAiy5N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFAiy5N.jpg&h=5f7ecb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第4分鐘，奧蘭多城就早早取得進球。米勒中路分球，迪科禁區右側低射遠角破門，1-0。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZQRT53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZQRT53.gif&h=c420cc1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20分鐘時，納什維爾扳平比分。在角球進攻中，洛維茨外圍左腳射門被擋出，他立刻右腳再射轟入世界波。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTAynZx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTAynZx.gif&h=7cad2062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在第61分鐘時，拿尼射進了一個精彩的罰球。在禁區弧左側，拿尼右腳搓出美妙弧線，皮球飛入近端死角。拿尼出生於1986年11月17日，下週他就將迎來34歲生日。但葡萄牙人卻顯得相當中二，他染了一頭紫髮，進球後做出龜波氣功慶祝動作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uh9CPE1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuh9CPE1.gif&h=a40c0113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrB2gj4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrB2gj4.gif&h=f552225c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿尼高興得有點早，納什維爾在終場前連進兩球完成大逆轉。88分鐘穆伊爾左路傳中，穆赫塔爾小禁區中路高高躍起頭球破門。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waaiy63.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwaaiy63.gif&h=a4f0e480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n93分鐘時，納什維爾上演了壓哨絕殺。穆赫塔爾右路角球傳中，卡迪茲近距離大力頭槌破門。卡迪茲是一名1米91的委內瑞拉高中鋒，他曾在法甲第戎效力過。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ChQuFM9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChQuFM9.gif&h=5b14ddba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d65008d29058f88e9caf3765cffe5952ee38e9a1","tid":2278174,"uid":34952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:44:46.000Z","msg":"新C朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cb9a221c53f5ee7f860124f99d0b13292a0c87","tid":2278174,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"Nani!?"},{"pid":"bf2bb1918029ca7ae23bb8434faeeedf4a28c3e8","tid":2278174,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36cb9a221c53f5ee7f860124f99d0b13292a0c87","tid":2278174,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"Nani!?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"Nani"},{"pid":"2f78df140e9170eed0a608b9c00af88034f97b84","tid":2278174,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:16:46.000Z","msg":"原來美職有得入場睇波，唔怪得爆到7彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c81db8e5b569f2bd350fea13dacf15ffd39e364","tid":2278174,"uid":27324,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"剩係會諗起佢呢球<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dvzPFEIJyoY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdvzPFEIJyoY&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2Baf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=28f0eefc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dvzPFEIJyoY</a>"},{"pid":"ab4f9702e9e29191fbcf16f98f18339482c6ff7b","tid":2278174,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"諗起pro club D撚屌8x分鐘入波high到癲左<br />\n之後補時俾人連入兩球反勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3f556b58725719dca4b9ebe6115765e7cc5a43","tid":2278174,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"美職而家水平同意甲差唔多<br />\n幾好睇"},{"pid":"dbc57d44a76ba74